You can write helper functions to invoke a series of slightly different tests:
```dart
void genGradle35AppBundleTest(String mode) {
  testUsingContext(...);
}
genGradle35AppBundleTest('debug');
genGradle35AppBundleTest('profile');
genGradle35AppBundleTest('release');
```

